.cs 4 on
.item 'PATCH CORE Command' 'Based on 10/75 ORVYL Manual'
.ix 'PC Command' . 'see PATCH CORE Command'
.boxon
PATCH CORE location-expression {hex-expression|'char string'}
           [VERIFY\{hex-expression|'char\string'}|NOVERIFY]
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
The PATCH CORE command changes the value at the specified core location.  The
VERIFY option causes ORVYL to abort the patch if the string does not match the
current contents of the location.  If neither VERIFY nor NOVERIFY is
specified, ORVYL indicates the previous value of the patched location.  The
NOVERIFY option causes this message to be suppressed.
.cs 4 off
